filter="collection_epoch=value". Collection_epoch can not be repeated. Value should be, eg (start_time,). Start time for historical data, unit is epoch time. Default value is "0", returns all historical data for requested interval or sample of minimal unit in db. End time for historical data, value is current epoch time.
